data.description: Welcome to this well cared for, 3-Bedroom 2-bath home that blends comfort and convenience in this fantastic location in New Braunfels Texas. Situated on a spacious corner lot, this gem is ready for you to make it your own. Inside, you'll find a thoughtfully designed layout, offering ample space for living and entertaining. The open-concept living area is bathed in natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The heart of this home is the well-appointed kitchen, complete with modern appliances and plenty of counter space for your culinary adventures. Imagine whipping up your favorite meals while staying connected with loved ones in the adjoining Dining Area and Breakfast Bar. When it's time to unwind, retreat to the Serene Bedrooms, including a spacious Master Suite with its own private bath. With two additional bedrooms, on the opposite side of the home, there's plenty of room for any living situation. But that's not all! Step outside to your expansive yard, perfect for outdoor gatherings, gardening, or simply enjoying the Texas sunshine. And let's not forget the unbeatable location – you're just moments away from shopping, restaurants, and all the wonderful amenities New Braunfels has to offer. Don't miss out on this opportunity to embrace the New Braunfels lifestyle and make this house your new home sweet home!
